Nakheel PJSC expects revenue from
malls and hotels to reach two billion dirhams ($544 million) by
the end of 2014 as several retail projects are completed,  Al
Bayan  newspaper reported, citing the companyâ€™s chairman.  Revenue from malls may reach 500 million dirhams by the end
of this year, Ali Rashed Lootah said, according to the report.
The Dubai-based  developer  has announced several retail and
entertainment projects such as Dragon Mall extension and The
